<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>*<sp/>@brief<sp/>Provides<sp/>utility<sp/>functions<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>nusol<sp/>module<sp/>in<sp/>CUDA.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>*/</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#ifndef<sp/>CU_NUSOL_UTILS_H</highlight></codeline>
